suing information research, and partner with government or private entities for research. The Director evaluates applications based on fostering collaborations, supporting students in information research, and partnering with government or private entities. The National Science Foundation authorizes appropriations for the Center, with annual meetings to promote collaboration among participants. The National Science Foundation authorizes appropriations for the Center as follows:
